{"prompt": "Generate a website for a custom metal fabrication shop. The aesthetic should be robust, using an industrial safety yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Metal Fabrication</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Industrial Safety Yellow */\n            color: #000;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #ccad00;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #FFD700;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #FFD700;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .services ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .services li {\n            background-color: #fff8dc; /* A softer yellow/beige */\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #FFD700;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .services li:hover {\n            background-color: #fff0b3;\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #FFD700;\n        }\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Apex Metal Fabrication</h1>\n        <p>Precision. Strength. Reliability.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>At Apex Metal Fabrication, we specialize in transforming raw metal into high-quality, custom-engineered solutions. With years of experience and a commitment to excellence, we serve a diverse range of industries, providing durable and precise metal components.</p>\n\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services\">\n            <ul>\n                <li>Custom Welding & Repair</li>\n                <li>Sheet Metal Fabrication</li>\n                <li>Structural Steel Work</li>\n                <li>Metal Prototyping</li>\n                <li>Machining & Finishing</li>\n                <li>Design Consultation</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>\n        <p>We pride ourselves on our attention to detail, robust craftsmanship, and unwavering dedication to meeting client specifications. Our industrial safety yellow accents symbolize our commitment to safety, visibility, and the robust nature of our work.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"contact-info\">\n        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+11234567890\">(123) 456-7890</a></p>\n        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@apexmetalfab.com\">info@apexmetalfab.com</a></p>\n        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Industrial Drive, Steel City, SC 54321</p>\n    </div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}